---
// Post-purchase confirmation page
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You — Your Guide is Ready | securemycameras.com</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: #FAFAF9;
            color: #1C1917;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #E7E5E4;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 48px 40px;
            max-width: 520px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.07), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .check {
            width: 64px; height: 64px;
            background: #ECFDF5;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #059669;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .sub {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #57534E;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .download-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 36px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.3);
        }
        .download-btn:hover {
            background: #047857;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .note {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #A8A29E;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #E7E5E4;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .cross-sell {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #57534E;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .cross-sell a {
            color: #DC2626;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .cross-sell a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .card { padding: 32px 24px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="check">&#10003;</div>
        <h1>You're all set.</h1>
        <p class="sub">Your Secure Camera Setup Guide is ready to download. Follow it start to finish — it takes about 30 minutes per camera.</p>

        <a href="/api/download" class="download-btn">
            Download Your Guide (PDF)
        </a>

        <p class="note">
            Check your email for a receipt from Paddle. Save this page if you need to re-download later.
        </p>

        <hr class="divider">

        <p class="cross-sell">
            Responsible for AI or cybersecurity policy at your company?<br>
            Check out the <a href="https://salishsecurity.ai">AI Security Policy Template Pack</a> — built for IT and security leaders at companies adopting AI.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
